                <description>
                  A right triangle with one of the acute angles labeled alpha and the other acute angle labeled beta.  The side opposite alpha is labeled <m>10</m> and the side opposite beta is labeled <m>8</m>.  The hypotenuse is labeled <m>r</m>.
